{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 313453, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那美院呢…", "timestamp": 1599199328, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313456, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那音辅呢...", "timestamp": 1599199362, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313458, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一号来清华是来学有机合成的？", "timestamp": 1599199385, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313459, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你来清华是刷GPA的？", "timestamp": 1599199391, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313472, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "只能说中国文艺就得靠这种特殊群体，高中通过特长生进入清华，然后到清华继续为文艺做贡献。如果没有这些优惠政策，中国的文艺界可能会更差...", "timestamp": 1599199506, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313474, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我支持给艺术团评奖，但是自带保研名额就很无理吧，要保应该保到艺术专业而不是任选", "timestamp": 1599199521, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313483, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "利益相关：艺术团成员（非特长生）", "timestamp": 1599199593, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313489, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: ++", "timestamp": 1599199669, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313494, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 但是你都保研经管了还跟艺术界有什么关系，", "timestamp": 1599199710, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313497, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 在理，保研任选专业就很扯", "timestamp": 1599199754, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313507, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "而且，在中国，艺术是政治化的，对于艺术团骨干来说，国家有什么政治任务需要他们他们就必须去，所以国家给予了他们一些优惠政策。你说这合不合理呢？我觉得在现行体质下完全合理。如果哪一天国家没有这些政治艺术了，这种东西可能才能取消吧", "timestamp": 1599199959, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313537, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 太对了，每年磨大赛（盲目追求难度）&各种zz演出（走台/换曲子一大堆）占用了大量时间，很多音乐性的东西很多寒暑训排了却全无演出机会", "timestamp": 1599200748, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313539, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "艺术团成员（非特长生）", "timestamp": 1599200765, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313540, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "*利益相关", "timestamp": 1599200772, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313561, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 为什么你们不去艺术学院？？所以就占了本专业学生的名额去读研？你觉得合适吗？有艺术理想去音乐学院美院不好吗？", "timestamp": 1599201184, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313570, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: 1. 要喷就喷制度，请不要喷艺术团成员；2. 很多人确实申请了艺术院校；3. 谁说艺术团骨干就要有艺术理想了？只不过是一种特长而已，而国家需要有这种特长的人来撑起其艺术上的门面", "timestamp": 1599201425, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313675, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 没有有艺术学硕士谢谢，咱又不是美院保了经管……", "timestamp": 1599203636, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313737, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: 请喷为什么国家不取消综合性大学艺术团（极其大赛评奖机制），不要喷艺术团成员", "timestamp": 1599204789, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 313801, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 62168, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 好吧，你可以认为我是在喷这种保研方式", "timestamp": 1599205488, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 62168, "reply": 19, "tag": null, "text": "#62166\n有一说一，你来清华是学音乐的？", "timestamp": 1599199291, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782613, "url": "", "vote": {}}}